<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Series Tracker — nunca mais perca o episódio</title>
<meta name="description" content="Series Tracker: acompanhe o que você está assistindo, episódio por episódio.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg: #10121B;
    --surface: #1A1D2B;
    --surface-2: #232739;
    --text: #F4F2ED;
    --text-dim: #8C90A6;
    --accent: #3DA5F5;
    --accent-dim: #1D4A73;
    --line: #2A2E42;
  }

  *{ margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  html{ scroll-behavior:smooth; }

  body{
    background:var(--bg);
    color:var(--text);
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    line-height:1.5;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }

  .wrap{
    max-width:1080px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:0 24px;
  }

  .mono{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  h1,h2,h3{
    font-family:'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;
    background:rgba(16,18,27,0.85);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  nav .wrap{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    height:64px;
  }
  .logo{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    font-family:'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:18px;
  }
  .logo-mark{
    width:28px; height:28px;
    border-radius:7px;
    object-fit:contain;
    display:block;
  }
  .nav-cta{
    font-size:14px;
    font-weight:600;
    color:var(--bg);
    background:var(--accent);
    padding:9px 18px;
    border-radius:8px;
    text-decoration:none;
    transition:filter .15s ease;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover{ filter:brightness(1.1); }

  /* HERO */
  header.hero{
    padding:96px 0 72px;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  header.hero::before{
    content:"";
    position:absolute;
    top:-200px; right:-200px;
    width:600px; height:600px;
    background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(61,165,245,0.12), transparent 70%);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size:13px;
    color:var(--accent);
    background:rgba(242,169,59,0.08);
    border:1px solid var(--accent-dim);
    padding:6px 12px;
    border-radius:100px;
    margin-bottom:28px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{
    content:"";
    width:6px; height:6px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--accent);
  }
  h1.headline{
    font-size:clamp(38px, 6vw, 64px);
    font-weight:700;
    line-height:1.05;
    max-width:780px;
    margin-bottom:24px;
  }
  h1.headline em{
    font-style:normal;
    color:var(--accent);
  }
  .subhead{
    font-size:18px;
    color:var(--text-dim);
    max-width:520px;
    margin-bottom:40px;
  }
  .hero-actions{
    display:flex; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap;
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  .btn-primary{
    background:var(--accent);
    color:#161616;
    font-weight:600;
    font-size:15px;
    padding:14px 26px;
    border-radius:10px;
    text-decoration:none;
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    transition:transform .15s ease, filter .15s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover{ transform:translateY(-1px); filter:brightness(1.08); }
  .btn-secondary{
    color:var(--text);
    font-weight:600;
    font-size:15px;
    padding:14px 26px;
    border-radius:10px;
    text-decoration:none;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    transition:border-color .15s ease, background .15s ease;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover{ border-color:var(--text-dim); background:var(--surface); }

  /* SIGNATURE: episode progress grid */
  .grid-panel{
    background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:32px;
  }
  .grid-panel-head{
    display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:space-between;
    margin-bottom:22px;
    flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px;
  }
  .grid-panel-title{
    font-size:14px;
    color:var(--text-dim);
  }
  .grid-panel-title .show{
    color:var(--text);
    font-weight:600;
  }
  .grid-panel-count{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size:13px;
    color:var(--accent);
  }
  .ep-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(24, 1fr);
    gap:5px;
  }
  .ep{
    aspect-ratio:1;
    border-radius:3px;
    background:var(--surface-2);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .ep.watched{
    background:var(--accent);
    border-color:var(--accent);
    opacity:calc(0.55 + (var(--i) * 0.02));
  }
  .ep.current{
    background:transparent;
    border:1.5px solid var(--accent);
    animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse{
    0%,100%{ box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(61,165,245,0.4); }
    50%{ box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(61,165,245,0); }
  }
  .grid-legend{
    display:flex; gap:20px; margin-top:20px;
    font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim);
  }
  .grid-legend span{ display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; }
  .legend-dot{ width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:2px; }
  .legend-dot.w{ background:var(--accent); }
  .legend-dot.c{ border:1.5px solid var(--accent); }
  .legend-dot.u{ background:var(--surface-2); border:1px solid var(--line); }

  @media (max-width:640px){
    .ep-grid{ grid-template-columns:repeat(12, 1fr); }
  }

  /* FEATURES */
  section.features{
    padding:96px 0;
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .section-label{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size:13px;
    color:var(--accent);
    margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  h2.section-title{
    font-size:clamp(28px, 4vw, 38px);
    font-weight:700;
    max-width:600px;
    margin-bottom:56px;
  }
  .feature-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap:1px;
    background:var(--line);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:14px;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .feature{
    background:var(--bg);
    padding:32px 28px;
  }
  .feature-tag{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size:12px;
    color:var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  .feature h3{
    font-size:19px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }
  .feature p{
    font-size:14.5px;
    color:var(--text-dim);
  }
  @media (max-width:800px){
    .feature-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  }

  /* HOW IT WORKS */
  section.how{
    padding:0 0 96px;
  }
  .steps{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:0;
  }
  .step{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;
    gap:24px;
    padding:28px 0;
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .step:last-child{ border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .step-num{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size:14px;
    color:var(--accent);
    padding-top:2px;
  }
  .step h3{
    font-size:18px;
    margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .step p{
    color:var(--text-dim);
    font-size:14.5px;
    max-width:460px;
  }

  /* CTA */
  section.cta{
    padding:80px 0 100px;
    text-align:center;
  }
  section.cta h2{
    font-size:clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px);
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  section.cta p{
    color:var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom:32px;
    font-size:16px;
  }

  footer{
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:32px 0;
  }
  footer .wrap{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px;
  }
  footer .foot-left{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim);
  }
  footer a{
    color:var(--text-dim);
    text-decoration:none;
    font-size:13px;
  }
  footer a:hover{ color:var(--text); }
  .foot-links{ display:flex; gap:24px; }

  ::selection{ background:var(--accent); color:#161616; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="icon.png" alt="Series Tracker" class="logo-mark">
      Series Tracker
    </div>
    <a class="nav-cta" href="#cta">Baixar app</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow">Disponível para Android</span>
    <h1 class="headline">Saiba exatamente <em>onde você parou</em> em cada série</h1>
    <p class="subhead">O Series Tracker guarda seu progresso episódio por episódio, pra você nunca mais perder o fio da meada entre uma temporada e outra.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="#cta">Ver na Google Play →</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="#como-funciona">Como funciona</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-label">O QUE ELE FAZ:</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Pensado pra quem assiste várias séries ao mesmo tempo</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-tag mono">01</div>
        <h3>Progresso por episódio</h3>
        <p>Marque cada episódio assistido e veja de relance quanto falta pra terminar a temporada.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-tag mono">02</div>
        <h3>Várias séries, uma tela</h3>
        <p>Organize tudo que você está assistindo, já terminou ou quer começar, sem misturar o progresso.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-tag mono">03</div>
        <h3>Retome sem esforço</h3>
        <p>Voltou depois de meses? O app te mostra exatamente o próximo episódio, sem precisar lembrar.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how" id="como-funciona">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-label">COMO FUNCIONA:</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Três passos, sem complicação.</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num mono">01</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Adicione a série</h3>
          <p>Procure o título e adicione à sua lista de acompanhamento.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num mono">02</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Marque o que já viu</h3>
          <p>Toque nos episódios conforme for assistindo, temporada por temporada.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num mono">03</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Continue de onde parou.</h3>
          <p>Abra o app quando quiser assistir de novo e veja direto qual é o próximo episódio.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta" id="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Comece a acompanhar suas séries hoje!</h2>
    <p>Gratuito, disponível na Google Play para Android.</p>
    <a class="btn-primary" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.seriestracker.app">Baixar na Google Play →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="foot-left">
      <img src="icon.png" alt="Series Tracker" class="logo-mark" style="width:22px;height:22px;">
      Series Tracker
    </div>
    <div class="foot-links">
      <a href="seriestrackeraplicativo@gmail.com">Contato</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
